quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,to is se barh kar zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot bolay aur sachhi baat jab is ke paas poanch jaye to usay jhutlaye .kiya jahannum mein kafiroon ka thikana nahi hai ?
  39,33,aur jo shakhs sachhi baat le kar aaya aur jis ne is ki tasdeeq ki wohi log mut-taqi hain
  39,34,woh jo chahain ge un ke liye un ke perwar-digaar ke paas ( mojood ) hai. naiko karon ka yahi badla hai
  39,35,taakay khuda un se buraiyon ko jo unhon ne kee daur kardey aur naik kamon ka jo woh karte rahay un ko badla day
  39,36,kiya khuda apne bundon ko kaafi nahi. aur yeh tum ko un logon se jo is ke siwa hain ( yani ghair khuda se ) darate hain. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere usay koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
  39,37,aur jis ko khuda hadaayat day is ko koi gumraah karne wala nahi.kiya khuda ghalib ( aur ) badla lainay wala nahi hai ?
  39,38,aur agar tum un se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya to keh den ke khuda ne. kaho ke bhala dekho to jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho. agar khuda mujh ko koi takleef p_hnchani chahay tokiya woh is takleef ko daur kar saktay hain ya agar mujh par meharbani karna chahay to woh is ki meharbani ko rok satke hain? keh do ke mujhe khuda hi kaafi hai. bharosa rakhnay walay isi par bharosa rakhtay hain
  39,39,keh do ke ae qoum tum apni jagah amal kiye jao mein ( apni jagah ) amal kiye jata hon. anqareeb tum ko maloom hojaye ga
  39,40,ke kis par azaab aata hai jo usay ruswa kere ga. aur kis par hamesha ka azaab nazil hota hai
